headline.print_headline: Obama Seeks to Allay Democrats' Fears on Obamacare
headline.main: Obama Seeks to Allay Democrats' Fears on Obamacare

lead_paragraph: President Barack Obama sought on Friday to ease strains with his Democratic allies in the U.S. Congress, who are fearful they could face election consequences from the botched rollout of the president's signature healthcare law known as "Obamacare."
